::Ramulus::

Ramulus looks at Spears as she stops, Ramulus also stopping. She didn't look 
like a traitorous bot, and there had been other ex-predacons in the Neo Beast 
Wars, most of which have since died for the Maximal cause. He shruggs.

"You looked pretty loyal screaming at a Pred to switch you for his hostage, 
I'm not going to make you leave," he sighs, "In fact, it would be better if 
you stayed. We'll need all the help we can get."
